飙速宅男 SPARE BIKE","summary":"「飙速宅男 SPARE BIKE 卷岛裕介」\r\n春天，卷岛裕介在总北高校入学。一直以来肚子骑车的他加入了总北自行车竞技部，自己自由的骑法得到周围的认同，能够在广阔的天空翱翔，使他满心雀跃。但他独特的舞蹈骑法，却遭到部里前辈们的嘲笑，并叫他改正骑法。而相信「自行车是自由的」的卷岛又将怎样……。\r\n「飙速宅男 SPARE BIKE 东堂尽八」\r\n追求美型时尚的初二学生东堂尽八，在箱根长大，是老铺温泉旅馆的嫡子。某一天，骑着折叠式自行车的朋友糸川修作邀他骑车比赛，但被他以戴头盔会弄乱发型为由拒绝。但2人在箱根的山上尝试比赛后，东堂心中却产生了一种冲动……。","nsfw":false,"date":"2016-09-09","platform":"其他","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/e0/3b/182702_SEpF8.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/e0/3b/182702_SEpF8.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/e0/3b/182702_SEpF8.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/e0/3b/182702_SEpF8.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/e0/3b/182702_SEpF8.jpg"},"infobox":[{"key":"wiki","value":"{{Infobox animanga/Movie\r\n|中文名= 飙速宅男 SPARE BIKE\r\n|别名={\r\n}\r\n|上映年度= 2016年9月9日\r\n|片长= \r\n|官方网站= http://yowapeda.com/sparebike/\r\n|其他= \r\n|Copyright= 渡辺航(週間少年チャンピオン)/弱虫ペダルSB製作委員会\r\n|美术监督= 李凡善\r\n|CG监督= 佐々木俊宏\r\n|话数= 1\r\n}}"}],"volumes":0,"eps":1,"total_episodes":1,"rating":{"rank":4137,"total":68,"score":6.4,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":1,"5":8,"6":28,"7":21,"8":8,"9":0,"10":1}},"collection":{"wish":52,"collect":135,"doing":9,"on_hold":8,"dropped":19},"tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":32},{"name":"2016","count":18},{"name":"运动","count":13},{"name":"漫画改","count":10},{"name":"2016年9月","count":8},{"name":"热血","count":7},{"name":"漫改","count":4},{"name":"竞技","count":4},{"name":"山下大輝","count":4},{"name":"日本","count":4},{"name":"TMS","count":4}],"meta_tags":["剧场版"]},"episodes":[{"id":801061,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","airdate":"","duration":"","type":0,"desc":""}],"updatedAt":"2026-05-02T07:20:10.115Z"},"182784":{"detail":{"id":182784,"type":2,"name":"GON -ゴン- 2期","name_cn":"小恐龙阿贡 第二季","summary":"","nsfw":false,"date":"2015-04-04","platform":"其他","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/d7/18/182784_u1916.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/d7/18/182784_u1916.jpg","large":"https://lain.